## 3. User Roles & Access Levels

### 3.1 Student

| Capability | Details |
|---|---|
| Register | Create account with student ID, email, password, fingerprint passphrase |
| Login | Authenticate with email + password |
| View Elections | See all active and upcoming elections |
| Cast Vote | After fingerprint verification, vote for one candidate per election |
| View Results | See published election results (bar chart / table) |

**Restrictions:**
- Cannot create or manage elections
- Cannot add candidates
- Cannot publish results
- Cannot vote twice in the same election (enforced on-chain)

### 3.2 Admin

| Capability | Details |
|---|---|
| Register | Create admin account using the secret key |
| Login | Authenticate with email + password |
| Create Election | Define election title, description, dates, and deploy a smart contract |
| Add Candidates | Add candidate details to an election |
| Manage Election Status | Start, end, or cancel elections |
| Publish Results | Read final tallies from the smart contract and publish to students |
| Approve Students | Approve or reject student registrations |

**Restrictions:**
- Cannot cast votes

